==English==

===Noun===
'''backpacker''' (Plural '''backpackers''')

# A traveller who carries their personal belongings in a [[knapsack]] strapped to their back.

# <i>Chiefly New Zealand.</i> An inexpensive place to stay, often with small dorm rooms of 4-8 beds shared by unrelated parties; [[hostel]]. 

====Usage notes====
Typically implies that the person is a [[budget]] traveller using [[hostel]]s and [[public transport]].

